{"tid":1324461,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"真‧被捕處理手法","createTime":"2019-07-16T14:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T19:05:44.000Z","uid":49083,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"193b1c256fff215f7043465f11a416569689b7f6","tid":1324461,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:38:25.000Z","msg":"我，本人親自問左律師 <br />\n0) 出門前講定比朋友家人知，過左某時間就幫自己搵定律師，因為依家狗係全力令你搵唔到人幫<br />\n1) 如果比人拉, 唔講野最好<br />\n2) 第一時間叫家人搵律師<br />\n3) 做唔到1,2 ，就算簽左簡易認罪，出到黎第一時間用錄音record自己記得既被捕到審問細節，同時搵律師，勁詳細講被捉及審問過程，律師先有機會幫到手<br />\n4) 就算48小時內咩事都無，都要搵定律師/法援<br />\n<br />\n總之記到既就要講同記錄低同一定要搵律師。"},{"pid":"bf0c380c1baaa45600b9214726378a76733324da","tid":1324461,"uid":209543,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:40:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"767bb4a01232e52a64990a1312d7d3a4c25f604e","tid":1324461,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁都負皮我...."},{"pid":"2adc59c245f558216322ed4c40b40455a9709dc0","tid":1324461,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:42:39.000Z","msg":"簡易認罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d2cc9ea13e72c363947124ccf1cd994f759837","tid":1324461,"uid":49083,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"2adc59c245f558216322ed4c40b40455a9709dc0","tid":1324461,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:42:39.000Z","msg":"簡易認罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:45:03.000Z","msg":"我特登問埋架...<br />\n如果簽左，就只可以打係有壓力/外在因素下被認罪<br />\n但一定要夠快，唔係個官都幫你唔到"},{"pid":"f68a736fad924df255122f9c83b5812fcf6172ce","tid":1324461,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re