我無野講 2.我要見律師<br />\n3.！！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">絕不解鎖</span>！！(repeat:！ 我無野講！無證據證明部電話係你既）<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察 被捕須知懶人包：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XLSCy9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XLSCy9&d=4wcocBccBPvk8MIeFEbr%2BcIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=e39908dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2XLSCy9</a><br />\n<br />\n法政匯思 截停與搜身懶人包：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Xi8hRI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Xi8hRI&d=4wcocBccBPvk8MIeFEbr%2BcIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=1ce373fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Xi8hRI</a><br />\n<br />\n法夢 入屋搜查懶人包：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Xk2FpM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Xk2FpM&d=4wcocBccBPvk8MIeFEbr%2BcIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=0848439d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Xk2FpM</a><br />\n<br />\n警察 截停 扣留及搜查的權力 各位請背一背<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1204239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1204239</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n身份證記住要用 RFID 卡套！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1282690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1282690</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n律師有野講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1323465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1323465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，我係2016年畀警犬資訊科技罪案組拘捕嘅肥菜，同大家講幾句<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1281607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1281607</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n被上門拘捕時，心理經驗分享（面書轉載）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1285556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1285556</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我俾人拉過 有啲嘢想講（有落口供實用資料）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1286561\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1286561</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n被捕由頭到尾，個人經驗可以入黎睇睇，信我實無事！請推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1282603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1282603</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n被捕須知，經驗之談，希望大家用唔著<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284802\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284802</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[唔好問我點解知] 畀狗咬上門 注意事項<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1283226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1283226</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a39150523d1beace1416c2c76cd24bd56e456eec","tid":1324461,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c372cf1ed2eb36a07fc39f3cd264119a7fc055a3","tid":1324461,"uid":49083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"13643df7a394153d655726aeee9a599815e29813","tid":1324461,"uid":23873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c5d2cc9ea13e72c363947124ccf1cd994f759837","tid":1324461,"uid":49083,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:45:03.000Z","msg":"我特登問埋架...<br />\n如果簽左，就只可以打係有壓力/外在因素下被認罪<br />\n但一定要夠快，唔係個官都幫你唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:40:33.000Z","msg":"打死都唔簽啦吓話"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:00:45.000Z","msg":"你睇下班狗告示威者咩？揾唔到證據就告人襲警，你估個小朋友比人打成點？迫成點？下一個到女仔呢？<br />\n<br />\n佢地面對緊既壓力你想像到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:48:14.000Z","msg":"咁都唔應該簽啦？<br />\n萬一個官唔接納你的講法咪仆街？"},{"pid":"1eb6fd1b2f5be9bc15cacd3b7a2302f2793a5fd5","tid":1324461,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:05:44.000Z","msg":"被捕需知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1202229\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1202229</a>"}]}